summary: FBI report regarding Rolando L. Cubela y Secades and a potential plan to eliminate Fidel Castro. The report discusses Cubela's contact with the CIA through Carlos Tepedino and concerns about providing Cubela with equipment. It also mentions a plan to kill Fidel Castro, which was allegedly reconsidered with President Johnson's knowledge.
title: Rolando L. Cubela Y Secades - IS - CUBA
